{"tid":1173409,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【？】華為任正非：若中國抵制蘋果，他第一個反對！","createTime":"2019-05-27T05:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T06:49:08.000Z","uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3c605a2a59349fce68cc4a23bb9168c4ac0f3676","tid":1173409,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:53:44.000Z","msg":"華為任正非：若中國抵制蘋果，他第一個反對！<br />\n<br />\n如果中國對蘋果公司(Apple Inc., AAPL)的產品實施反制性禁令，蘋果公司或受到沉重打擊，不過，華為技術有限公司(Huawei Technologies Co.)創辦人兼首席執行長任正非認為不會出現這種情況。<br />\n<br />\n在彭博電視(Bloomberg Television)周日進行的訪問中，任正非表示，他會反對這樣的措施。任正非向彭博電視表示，首先，這一定不會發生；但如果發生了，他第一個反對。蘋果是他的老師，處在領導者地位，作為學生怎會反咬老師一口呢？他從來不會這樣做。<br />\n<br />\n上周，高盛警告如果中國停止進口蘋果公司產品，該公司每股收益可能受到29%的衝擊。任正非承認，特朗普(Donald Trump)政府針對華為產品的進口禁令可能在短期內衝擊這家中國科技巨頭，但實際影響將取決於華為在多快的時間裡度過這個磨合階段。<br />\n<br />\n（本文譯自MarketWatch）"},{"pid":"537491b64545e5b19137c12b5214ed35a0e0d95f","tid":1173409,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:54:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%BB%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%9E%E8%8B%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E4%BB%96%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-045320275.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E9%259D%259E%25E8%258B%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258A%25B5%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E4%25BB%2596%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D-045320275.html&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWHqIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=395996be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%BB%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%9E%E8%8B%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E4%BB%96%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-045320275.html</a>"},{"pid":"fe5c5c7438acc35aea1f7d497c55ef73bceb6cff","tid":1173409,"uid":54337,"like":6,"dis